Predict Claim Denial / Payment Risk (Supervised Learning)
Goal: Build a model that predicts whether a healthcare claim will be denied or paid late.
Software: Orange

Relevant for healthcare finance / revenue cycle / payer analytics work.

Example Target
claim_denied = Yes / No

Example Features/Data Fields
  payer type
  service category
  diagnosis count
  CPT category
  place of service
  claim amount
  provider specialty
  prior denial history
  submission lag days


Use the same core workflow as Project 1 (Supervised Learning project → Outcome Prediction):

File → Select Columns → Impute → Continuize → Rank → Logistic Regression / Tree / Random Forest → Test & Score → Confusion Matrix → ROC Analysis

Business Value:
Frame the project as:

  identifying denial risk earlier
  reducing rework
  improving reimbursement cycle
  prioritizing claims for manual review
